OL,3,CBoy drowned in holiday park pool after
OL,4,Cbeing separated from parents
OL,6,FA five-year-old boy drowned in a
OL,7,Fholiday park swimming pool after
OL,8,Fbecoming separated from his parents,
OL,9,Fan inquest has heard.
OL,11,FRobin Caliskan, from Plymouth, died in
OL,12,FJuly last year while on a family
OL,13,Fholiday in Cornwall.
OL,15,FHe was found face down at the bottom
OL,16,Fof the pool at Atlantic Reach Holiday
OL,17,FPark, near Newquay, by members of the
OL,18,Fpublic.
