OL,3,CBoy drowned in holiday park pool after
OL,4,Cbeing separated from parents
OL,6,FThe family had only arrived at the
OL,7,Fholiday park around an hour before
OL,8,FRobin's death, with the five-year-old
OL,9,Fexcitedly helping to pitch up their
OL,10,Ftent.
OL,12,FAn inquest hearing in Truro has heard
OL,13,Fhis parents then took Robin and his
OL,14,Fyounger brother, who was six months
OL,15,Fold at the time, for a swim at the
OL,16,Fcentre's indoor pool.
