OL,3,CBoy drowned in holiday park pool after
OL,4,Cbeing separated from parents
OL,6,FSpeaking through an interpreter,
OL,7,FRobin's father, Cemal Caliskan, an
OL,8,Felectrical engineer originally from
OL,9,FTurkey, said: "I looked at the big
OL,10,Fpool at first, it was very crowded,
OL,11,Fthere were adults and lots of
OL,12,Fchildren, when I saw the children
OL,13,Fswimming I thought: 'Fine,' so me and
OL,14,FRobin headed to the big pool."
OL,16,FHe said after about 10 minutes, he and
OL,17,FRobin went to the baby pool where they
OL,18,Fjoined his wife and other son and they
OL,19,Ftook a family photo together.
