OL,3,CBoy drowned in holiday park pool after
OL,4,Cbeing separated from parents
OL,6,FMr Caliskan continued: "I took our
OL,7,Flittle boy from my wife, I decided to
OL,8,Flook after him for a bit and I said to
OL,9,Fmy wife: 'If you want to go to the big
OL,10,Fpool, you can' and she decided to go
OL,11,Fin the big pool.
OL,13,F"Robin was just playing there, my wife
OL,14,Fwas heading to the big pool and Robin
OL,15,Fsaid: 'Can I go please?' He wanted to
OL,16,Fgo with my wife, his mum, and I said:
OL,17,F'OK, but you need to stay with your
OL,18,Fmum, go with your mum.'
OL,26,@nD@XOUuD@AOU
