OL,3,CBoy drowned in holiday park pool after
OL,4,Cbeing separated from parents
OL,6,F"Then he followed my wife. It was so
OL,7,Fcrowded in the big pool I can't be
OL,8,F100% sure if Robin was following my
OL,9,Fwife or beside her.
OL,11,F"I could just see my wife and there
OL,12,Fwas a child next to my wife and I
OL,13,Fthought that was Robin."
OL,15,FHe added: "I was sure he was with her."
OL,17,FMr Caliskan said that after a while,
OL,18,Fhis wife came back and they then
OL,19,Frealised that Robin wasn't there.
