OL,3,CBoy drowned in holiday park pool after
OL,4,Cbeing separated from parents
OL,6,FHe added: "We noticed that people had
OL,7,Ftaken someone out of the pool and they
OL,8,Fall gathered at one location and we
OL,9,Fdecided to go there as well. When I
OL,10,Farrived there I saw two people trying
OL,11,Fto give treatment to Robin."
OL,13,FThe inquest was shown photos of signs
OL,14,Fput up at the pool including sets of
OL,15,Frules posted in the men's and women's
OL,16,Fchanging rooms which stated: "No
OL,17,Flifeguard on duty", with a further
OL,18,Fsign stating the rule at the poolside.
