OL,3,CBoy drowned in holiday park pool after
OL,4,Cbeing separated from parents
OL,6,FMr Caliskan said he had not seen the
OL,7,Fsigns and added that he had seen
OL,8,Fphotos on Facebook which showed
OL,9,Flifeguards at the pool, and he had
OL,10,Fseen someone in a "red and yellow
OL,11,Foutfit" at the pool.
OL,13,FHe added: "I didn't see signs about
OL,14,Flifeguards, if I did see that I would
OL,15,Fdefinitely go back to reception and
OL,16,Fsay: 'I thought you had lifeguards?'
OL,17,Fand ask them questions.'"
